    calendars in your favourite app. <a href="{{ '/about/' | url | absoluteUrl(config.baseUrl) }}">Find out more</a>
</p>

<p class="subscribe">
    <a href="{{ '/events/' | url | absoluteUrl(config.baseUrl) | webcal }}">
